name: Spelunking, Swimming, And Over looking Manila at Tanay Day Tour
description: If you have a free day in Manila and are sick of your usual city tours, avail of a day tour in Tanay! Just a few hours away from the hustle and bustle of city life, you'll be able to swim in two different waterfalls, go spelunking in underground caves, and as a finale, watch the sun set over Manila.
